name: SVGMaskElement
description: The SVGMaskElement interface provides access to the properties of <mask> elements, as well as methods to manipulate them.

members.name: SVGMaskElement.maskUnits
members.description: An SVGAnimatedEnumeration corresponding to the maskUnits attribute of the given <mask> element. Takes one of the constants defined in SVGUnitTypes.

members.name: SVGMaskElement.maskContentUnits
members.description: An SVGAnimatedEnumeration corresponding to the maskContentUnits attribute of the given <mask> element. Takes one of the constants defined in SVGUnitTypes.

members.name: SVGMaskElement.x
members.description: An SVGAnimatedLength corresponding to the x attribute of the given <mask> element.

members.name: SVGMaskElement.y
members.description: An SVGAnimatedLength corresponding to the y attribute of the given <mask> element.

members.name: SVGMaskElement.width
members.description: An SVGAnimatedLength corresponding to the width attribute of the given <mask> element.

members.name: SVGMaskElement.height
members.description: An SVGAnimatedLength corresponding to the height attribute of the given <mask> element.
